Class Rectangle

java.lang.Object
  model.Shape
      model.Rectangle

public class Rectangle
extends Shape

This class is a subclass of Shape. It is used to draw lines to the Netpaint window whenever a Rectangle object is called.

Author:
TannerKoch, JamesDeveuve
